  <body>
    <div style="basic">
        <p begin="00:00:00.230" end="00:00:04.990" tts:direction="ltr">Hello, visitors. I want to share with you
<br />a bit of</p>
        <p begin="00:00:04.990" end="00:00:09.290" tts:direction="ltr">a story scenario regarding storytelling
<br />with data.</p>
        <p begin="00:00:09.290" end="00:00:12.430" tts:direction="ltr">I feel that I hear these types of stories</p>
        <p begin="00:00:12.430" end="00:00:16.750" tts:direction="ltr">from our former alum Aggies and also our
<br />interns.</p>
        <p begin="00:00:16.750" end="00:00:18.770" tts:direction="ltr">I thought it would be relevant to
<br />construct</p>
        <p begin="00:00:18.770" end="00:00:22.090" tts:direction="ltr">something that I believe you may
<br />encounter.</p>
        <p begin="00:00:22.090" end="00:00:27.290" tts:direction="ltr">I provided a PDF of the story handout that
<br />I'm going to go through today.</p>
        <p begin="00:00:27.290" end="00:00:29.810" tts:direction="ltr">It might be something that you just tuck
<br />into one of</p>
        <p begin="00:00:29.810" end="00:00:33.490" tts:direction="ltr">your folders and perhaps remember that you
<br />have</p>
        <p begin="00:00:33.490" end="00:00:36.390" tts:direction="ltr">and use it as a tool when you are</p>
        <p begin="00:00:36.390" end="00:00:40.490" tts:direction="ltr">encountered with a scenario maybe similar
<br />to this one.</p>
        <p begin="00:00:40.490" end="00:00:44.470" tts:direction="ltr">So we're going to start off with PAC,
<br />which I like to do,</p>
        <p begin="00:00:44.470" end="00:00:51.010" tts:direction="ltr">and that purpose is to convince a CMO to
<br />support a new campaign.</p>
        <p begin="00:00:51.010" end="00:00:53.090" tts:direction="ltr">You are interning for</p>
        <p begin="00:00:53.090" end="00:00:57.930" tts:direction="ltr">Aggie ice cream and you've got some data
<br />that you're working with,</p>
        <p begin="00:00:57.930" end="00:01:01.690" tts:direction="ltr">and you are reporting to a manager.</p>
        <p begin="00:01:01.690" end="00:01:03.730" tts:direction="ltr">That is who your audience is.</p>
        <p begin="00:01:03.730" end="00:01:05.210" tts:direction="ltr">Your audience is actually</p>
        <p begin="00:01:05.210" end="00:01:07.850" tts:direction="ltr">the manager of the division that you're
<br />interning under,</p>
        <p begin="00:01:07.850" end="00:01:10.135" tts:direction="ltr">and this manager is charismatic.</p>
        <p begin="00:01:10.135" end="00:01:13.100" tts:direction="ltr">And loves adding data to persuade.</p>
        <p begin="00:01:13.100" end="00:01:17.020" tts:direction="ltr">They're really coming to you as the data
<br />analyst intern</p>
        <p begin="00:01:17.020" end="00:01:22.760" tts:direction="ltr">to help them achieve their persuasive
<br />stories.</p>
        <p begin="00:01:22.760" end="00:01:24.780" tts:direction="ltr">Your data is credible.</p>
        <p begin="00:01:24.780" end="00:01:26.840" tts:direction="ltr">It was gathered by a third party through</p>
        <p begin="00:01:26.840" end="00:01:29.780" tts:direction="ltr">a consulting contract and</p>
        <p begin="00:01:29.780" end="00:01:33.360" tts:direction="ltr">it's been vetted and found to be
<br />statistically sound.</p>
        <p begin="00:01:33.360" end="00:01:39.580" tts:direction="ltr">Your kind is a bit of a road bump because
<br />your manager loves tables.</p>
        <p begin="00:01:39.580" end="00:01:41.400" tts:direction="ltr">Anytime you've to this point,</p>
        <p begin="00:01:41.400" end="00:01:47.610" tts:direction="ltr">try to encourage other chart kinds They
<br />have wanted to just default to tables,</p>
        <p begin="00:01:47.610" end="00:01:49.830" tts:direction="ltr">which gives me the sad face.</p>
        <p begin="00:01:49.830" end="00:01:53.710" tts:direction="ltr">But you will encounter some prejudices and</p>
        <p begin="00:01:53.710" end="00:01:57.250" tts:direction="ltr">some preferences with existing co workers</p>
        <p begin="00:01:57.250" end="00:02:00.170" tts:direction="ltr">or managers. You have to be aware of that.</p>
        <p begin="00:02:00.170" end="00:02:04.370" tts:direction="ltr">We're going to use that for this first
<br />part of this scenario A.</p>
        <p begin="00:02:04.370" end="00:02:08.110" tts:direction="ltr">Your manager comes to your desk to</p>
        <p begin="00:02:08.110" end="00:02:11.790" tts:direction="ltr">your cubicle and gives you this table and
<br />says,</p>
        <p begin="00:02:11.790" end="00:02:15.410" tts:direction="ltr">I have a meeting in 15 minutes with the
<br />CMO,</p>
        <p begin="00:02:15.410" end="00:02:18.990" tts:direction="ltr">and I would love to make this table
<br />better.</p>
        <p begin="00:02:18.990" end="00:02:24.730" tts:direction="ltr">Can you do anything? And like the eager
<br />intern you should be,</p>
        <p begin="00:02:24.730" end="00:02:26.410" tts:direction="ltr">the answer will be yes.</p>
        <p begin="00:02:26.410" end="00:02:28.670" tts:direction="ltr">You might be thinking, what can I do in</p>
        <p begin="00:02:28.670" end="00:02:32.210" tts:direction="ltr">15 minutes to make this table tell a
<br />story?</p>
        <p begin="00:02:32.210" end="00:02:36.470" tts:direction="ltr">I'm going to provide you with a potential
<br />pathway.</p>
        <p begin="00:02:36.470" end="00:02:42.470" tts:direction="ltr">The 15 minute fix starts off with some
<br />takeaway title.</p>
        <p begin="00:02:42.470" end="00:02:45.810" tts:direction="ltr">Spend five to even 7 minutes looking at</p>
        <p begin="00:02:45.810" end="00:02:50.065" tts:direction="ltr">the data to really understand what it's
<br />telling you.</p>
        <p begin="00:02:50.065" end="00:02:52.600" tts:direction="ltr">Then once that is apparent,</p>
        <p begin="00:02:52.600" end="00:02:54.780" tts:direction="ltr">create some takeaway title.</p>
        <p begin="00:02:54.780" end="00:03:00.040" tts:direction="ltr">In this case, I've written overall testers
<br />prefer Aggie ice cream.</p>
        <p begin="00:03:00.040" end="00:03:04.320" tts:direction="ltr">Now, we're comparing the strawberry
<br />flavors from both creameries.</p>
        <p begin="00:03:04.320" end="00:03:07.820" tts:direction="ltr">There is a sample size of 155,</p>
        <p begin="00:03:07.820" end="00:03:11.520" tts:direction="ltr">and then our standard deviation is 0.05.</p>
        <p begin="00:03:11.520" end="00:03:16.280" tts:direction="ltr">We feel highly confident that this is
<br />fairly accurate.</p>
        <p begin="00:03:16.280" end="00:03:22.200" tts:direction="ltr">I'm using that overall likene score of 7.1
<br />in relation to</p>
        <p begin="00:03:22.200" end="00:03:30.460" tts:direction="ltr">BYU creamery a 5.9 to support my
<br />preference verb that I've chosen.</p>
        <p begin="00:03:30.460" end="00:03:33.960" tts:direction="ltr">Now, another thing that you may or may not</p>
        <p begin="00:03:33.960" end="00:03:37.400" tts:direction="ltr">have noticed is that I have just taken</p>
        <p begin="00:03:37.400" end="00:03:45.120" tts:direction="ltr">a rectangle box and put it over all of the
<br />other variables to decrease those.</p>
        <p begin="00:03:45.120" end="00:03:51.200" tts:direction="ltr">I can emphasize the characteristic that
<br />I'm lifting out of this table.</p>
        <p begin="00:03:51.200" end="00:03:53.380" tts:direction="ltr">A pretty easy trick,</p>
        <p begin="00:03:53.380" end="00:03:57.400" tts:direction="ltr">but one where I can emphasize and</p>
        <p begin="00:03:57.400" end="00:04:02.705" tts:direction="ltr">create a little bit of that pre attentive
<br />attribute that we know is important.</p>
        <p begin="00:04:02.705" end="00:04:08.350" tts:direction="ltr">The other thing I would focus on doing is
<br />providing a little bit of context.</p>
        <p begin="00:04:08.350" end="00:04:12.490" tts:direction="ltr">You can see there's some copy right below
<br />that takeaway title that says,</p>
        <p begin="00:04:12.490" end="00:04:17.510" tts:direction="ltr">Let's discuss in a recent taste test of
<br />155 participants,</p>
        <p begin="00:04:17.510" end="00:04:19.610" tts:direction="ltr">Aggie ice cream strawberry flavor</p>
        <p begin="00:04:19.610" end="00:04:23.670" tts:direction="ltr">outperformed BLU creamery and overall
<br />liking scores.</p>
        <p begin="00:04:23.670" end="00:04:27.930" tts:direction="ltr">Then you can add other context here if it
<br />makes sense for the audience.</p>
        <p begin="00:04:27.930" end="00:04:30.750" tts:direction="ltr">Again, knowing your audience is important
<br />and maybe</p>
        <p begin="00:04:30.750" end="00:04:33.810" tts:direction="ltr">you would add another idea or two here.</p>
        <p begin="00:04:33.810" end="00:04:37.170" tts:direction="ltr">Finally, you would end with a question.</p>
        <p begin="00:04:37.170" end="00:04:41.810" tts:direction="ltr">What are the next steps to highlight these
<br />results in our marketing efforts?</p>
        <p begin="00:04:41.810" end="00:04:44.470" tts:direction="ltr">Really leading with that action,</p>
        <p begin="00:04:44.470" end="00:04:47.310" tts:direction="ltr">but framing it in a question.</p>
        <p begin="00:04:47.310" end="00:04:49.230" tts:direction="ltr">You've only got 15 minutes,</p>
        <p begin="00:04:49.230" end="00:04:56.575" tts:direction="ltr">but I feel like this would be a good
<br />conversation with a place to start?</p>
        <p begin="00:04:56.575" end="00:05:00.600" tts:direction="ltr">Now, if your boss were to come to you and
<br />say,</p>
        <p begin="00:05:00.600" end="00:05:03.040" tts:direction="ltr">you actually have 30 minutes,</p>
        <p begin="00:05:03.040" end="00:05:07.840" tts:direction="ltr">you might apply some additional design
<br />features</p>
        <p begin="00:05:07.840" end="00:05:10.100" tts:direction="ltr">to it to improve that storytelling.</p>
        <p begin="00:05:10.100" end="00:05:14.620" tts:direction="ltr">We still have our sample size of 155,</p>
        <p begin="00:05:14.620" end="00:05:18.560" tts:direction="ltr">but now I've removed all of those bars
