        <p begin="00:05:18.560" end="00:05:20.860" tts:direction="ltr">I've really cleaned this up,</p>
        <p begin="00:05:20.860" end="00:05:24.340" tts:direction="ltr">and then the next step is,</p>
        <p begin="00:05:24.340" end="00:05:28.355" tts:direction="ltr">I'm going to I've applied some white
<br />space.</p>
        <p begin="00:05:28.355" end="00:05:30.510" tts:direction="ltr">That's an important element.</p>
        <p begin="00:05:30.510" end="00:05:35.610" tts:direction="ltr">Now I'm going to apply some write
