        <p begin="00:05:44.830" end="00:05:48.450" tts:direction="ltr">so that I can just focus on the core word.</p>
        <p begin="00:05:48.450" end="00:05:52.250" tts:direction="ltr">You'll see here, I have overall
<br />capitalized</p>
        <p begin="00:05:52.250" end="00:05:56.605" tts:direction="ltr">and then the subsequent ones just in their
