        <p begin="00:06:02.900" end="00:06:05.580" tts:direction="ltr">and it looks like appearance is at the top
<br />there.</p>
        <p begin="00:06:05.580" end="00:06:10.240" tts:direction="ltr">I might want to even bold appearance so
