        <p begin="00:06:10.240" end="00:06:14.620" tts:direction="ltr">Maybe that's an attribute that we want to
<br />highlight in the marketing campaign,</p>
        <p begin="00:06:14.620" end="00:06:19.040" tts:direction="ltr">really showing our creamy strawberry ice
