        <p begin="00:06:23.935" end="00:06:26.750" tts:direction="ltr">I might even want to highlight</p>
        <p begin="00:06:26.750" end="00:06:32.590" tts:direction="ltr">some subsequent features like the tartness
<br />or sourness of the ice cream,</p>
        <p begin="00:06:32.590" end="00:06:33.990" tts:direction="ltr">the sweetness, the cream,</p>
        <p begin="00:06:33.990" end="00:06:38.150" tts:direction="ltr">the flavor, the dairy taste to it.</p>
        <p begin="00:06:38.150" end="00:06:43.030" tts:direction="ltr">Okay? All of this is just part of</p>
        <p begin="00:06:43.030" end="00:06:51.650" tts:direction="ltr">that iterative exploration to finally get
<br />to some sort of a better result.</p>
        <p begin="00:06:51.650" end="00:06:58.650" tts:direction="ltr">This is the 30 minute answer that has more
<br />story and design and more value.</p>
        <p begin="00:06:58.650" end="00:07:02.650" tts:direction="ltr">Here, the takeaway title is in reverse
<br />type</p>
        <p begin="00:07:02.650" end="00:07:06.750" tts:direction="ltr">with the blue on the back and the white
<br />white type.</p>
        <p begin="00:07:06.750" end="00:07:11.595" tts:direction="ltr">It says, Success, we outperform our
