<br />liking scores and taste.</p>
        <p begin="00:07:44.920" end="00:07:46.400" tts:direction="ltr">Then the discussion is,</p>
        <p begin="00:07:46.400" end="00:07:47.985" tts:direction="ltr">what are the next steps?</p>
        <p begin="00:07:47.985" end="00:07:50.390" tts:direction="ltr">This is the 30 minute fix.</p>
        <p begin="00:07:50.390" end="00:07:54.690" tts:direction="ltr">This is the 15 minute fix.</p>
        <p begin="00:07:54.690" end="00:07:57.970" tts:direction="ltr">But both of them are doing a much better
