        <p begin="00:08:07.430" end="00:08:10.010" tts:direction="ltr">You may still have to use tables.</p>
        <p begin="00:08:10.010" end="00:08:14.370" tts:direction="ltr">You may still have limited tools.</p>
        <p begin="00:08:14.370" end="00:08:16.110" tts:direction="ltr">You may have to only use Excel,</p>
        <p begin="00:08:16.110" end="00:08:20.290" tts:direction="ltr">but you can still use all of these
